sentences: Yang Chaoyue (Chinese: 杨超越, born July 31, 1998) is a Chinese actress and singer.
She was named by China Newsweek as one of the most influential Chinese people in 2018.
Yang was born on July 31, 1998, in a village in Dafeng, Yancheng, Jiangsu, China.
